{"tid":2206162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"避國安法　德自民黨關港辦公室","createTime":"2020-09-17T10:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T10:44:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c737000ffb8eacbff78a10f2051cc0e3816809b","tid":2206162,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"避國安法　德自民黨關港辦公室<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/09/FNF.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F09%2FFNF.html&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=e14b921f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/09/FNF.html</a><br />\n<br />\n跟德國自民黨（FDP）有關連的智庫Friedrich Naumann Foundation for Freedom（FNF）昨天16號發聲明宣佈，由香港國安法的關係，令其不能保證在港員工的安全，因此要把運作了只有約兩年的香港辦公室關閉，終止租用在港的辦公室，所有在港項目要暫停。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，已有一名員工以擔心個人安全為由，離開FNF，而為了餘下4名員工的安全，FNF也要跟結束跟他們的工作關係。<br />\nFNF的主席Karl-Heinz Paqu&eacute;稱，香港警察在8月26日的一輪拘捕（應該是指就元朗7.21事件拘捕兩名民主黨立法會議員林卓廷及許智峯，以及其他多人），影響了智庫的長期合作夥伴，在香港爭取民主和自由，會處於危險之中，智庫不能置其員工及夥伴於風險之中，因此結束在港辦公室。<br />\n<br />\nPaqu&eacute;說，智庫在香港的員工可以被指控為「外國代理人」，並因此判囚數年。他批評，誰是「外國代理人」，對國安有多大威脅，完全由中國當局隨意定奪。<br />\n<br />\nFNF在港辦公室，去年年中也捲入一場小小的中德外交風波。自民黨黨魁林德納（Christian Lindner）去年7月曾訪港，來過這個辦公室，有關照片上載至facebook，德國駐港總領事館也有分享。文首照片就是林德納（右四）在自己的Twitter上載、當時在港出席FNF活動的照片。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n全文請前往歐洲動態"},{"pid":"8ce490a9f28d0ccf3288c402c4c6b3e2c9fbac8c","tid":2206162,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f023f73806a7c135e2ab0b4e2afc978de9da576","tid":2206162,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615517ed5666becba13a86c15ca327487888cffb","tid":2206162,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2890e0b05f7999cd8892e570e79a324c561a65","tid":2206162,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e674902d42834461123d6076d0696232949e201a","tid":2206162,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}